	(1589,2020,'biographical_info','I recently earned my doctorate from the University of Southern Mississippi. My dissertation work investigated breeding development in songbirds during spring migration and incorporated research I conducted at AIMS. I have also worked at a <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.kristenmcovino.com/field-sites\">long-term field site in Louisiana</a> and I am an NABC certified bander and trainer. You can read more about me at my <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.kristenmcovino.com/\">personal website</a>.'),
