	(1682,2034,'biographical_info','I am a senior at Harvard College hoping to enter the world of education post-graduation. I am a captain of the wrestling team, and can\'t think of anything that I love more than wrestling, though birding is a close second. Fun fact: my mom cooks the food that we scarf down in fifteen minute intervals between net runs. '),
