	(1840,1,'2016-04-27 20:31:34','2016-04-27 20:31:34','Once you are on the <a href=\"#\">Volunteer Schedule</a>, you will need to do the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Email the <a href=\"mailto:Alexa Hilmer &lt;alh229@cornell.edu&gt;\">SML Island Coordinator</a> (Alexa Hilmer) to get on the <a href=\"http://www.shoalsmarinelaboratory.org/boat-schedule\">Boat Schedule</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Remember</strong>! The boat schedule is subject to change and should be considered tentative. Be sure to confirm with Alexa 1-2 days before you\'re scheduled to go out.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Complete the <a href=\"http://www.shoalsmarinelaboratory.org/sites/shoalsmarinelaboratory.org/files/media/pdf/VisitorForms/sml_researcher_forms_2016.pdf\">required forms</a> and return them to SML using either the snail mail address or fax number on the forms, OR by <a href=\"mailto:alh229@cornell.edu\">emailing them</a> to Alexa.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Note</strong>: all volunteers need to submit new forms before going out to Appledore, even if they submitted forms for a recent season.','Volunteer Checklist','','inherit','closed','closed','','1839-revision-v1','','','2016-04-27 20:31:34','2016-04-27 20:31:34','',1839,'http://burtonux.com/aims/2016/04/27/1839-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
